    {
      "id": "el_14",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 497,
      "width": 297,
      "height": 219,
      "text": "Filling pipe = POSITIVE (+)\nEmptying pipe = NEGATIVE (-)\nNet efficiency = Sum with signs\n\nnet>0 → fills   net<0 → empties\n\nLeak = (a×b)/(b-a)\na=without leak  b=with leak\n\nWHY: Fill rate - Leak rate = Net rate.\n  1/a - 1/leak = 1/b → solve for leak.\n\nEx: Pipe=8h, with leak=12h →\n  Leak = 8×12/(12-8) = 24h",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 1400,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 14,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "f3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Filling pipe = POSITIVE (+)\nEmptying pipe = NEGATIVE (-)\nNet efficiency = Sum with signs\n\nnet>0 → fills   net<0 → empties\n\nLeak = (a×b)/(b-a)\na=without leak  b=with leak\n\nWHY: Fill rate - Leak rate = Net rate.\n  1/a - 1/leak = 1/b → solve for leak.\n\nEx: Pipe=8h, with leak=12h →\n  Leak = 8×12/(12-8) = 24h",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
