    {
      "id": "el_31",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 892,
      "width": 274,
      "height": 288,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=1/10, B=1/12, C=1/15 per day\nStep 2: Together = 1/10+1/12+1/15\n  = 6/60+5/60+4/60 = 15/60 = 1/4\nStep 3: Time = 1 ÷ (1/4) = 4 days\n\nTRICK (LCM method):\nLCM(10,12,15) = 60 → A=6, B=5, C=4\n\n         (60) Total Work\n           |\n    -------+-------\n    |      |       |\n   (6)    (5)     (4)  ← 6+5+4=15/day\n  (10)   (12)    (15)\n    A      B       C\n\nTogether = 15/day → 60/15 = 4 days\n\nAnswer: 4 days ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 31,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_2"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=1/10, B=1/12, C=1/15 per day\nStep 2: Together = 1/10+1/12+1/15\n  = 6/60+5/60+4/60 = 15/60 = 1/4\nStep 3: Time = 1 ÷ (1/4) = 4 days\n\nTRICK (LCM method):\nLCM(10,12,15) = 60 → A=6, B=5, C=4\n\n         (60) Total Work\n           |\n    -------+-------\n    |      |       |\n   (6)    (5)     (4)  ← 6+5+4=15/day\n  (10)   (12)    (15)\n    A      B       C\n\nTogether = 15/day → 60/15 = 4 days\n\nAnswer: 4 days ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
