    {
      "id": "el_36",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 892,
      "width": 346,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Aman=1/30, Raman=1/20 per day\n  Together = 1/30+1/20 = 2/60+3/60 = 5/60 = 1/12\nStep 2: 10 days together = 10×(1/12) = 5/6 done\n  Remaining = 1-5/6 = 1/6\nStep 3: Aman alone: (1/6)÷(1/30) = 30/6 = 5 days\n\nTRICK (LCM method):\nLCM(30,20)=60 → Aman=2, Raman=3, Together=5\n\n|←── 10 days ──→|←── 5 days ──→|\n|  Aman + Raman  |  Aman alone  |\n|  5/day → 50    |  2/day → 5d  |\n\nLeft = 60-50 = 10 → 10/2 = 5 more days\n\nAnswer: 10 + 5 = 15 days ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 3600,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 36,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_3"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Aman=1/30, Raman=1/20 per day\n  Together = 1/30+1/20 = 2/60+3/60 = 5/60 = 1/12\nStep 2: 10 days together = 10×(1/12) = 5/6 done\n  Remaining = 1-5/6 = 1/6\nStep 3: Aman alone: (1/6)÷(1/30) = 30/6 = 5 days\n\nTRICK (LCM method):\nLCM(30,20)=60 → Aman=2, Raman=3, Together=5\n\n|←── 10 days ──→|←── 5 days ──→|\n|  Aman + Raman  |  Aman alone  |\n|  5/day → 50    |  2/day → 5d  |\n\nLeft = 60-50 = 10 → 10/2 = 5 more days\n\nAnswer: 10 + 5 = 15 days ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
