      "width": 360,
      "height": 260,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=1/12, B=1/18 per day\n  B worked all 10 days = 10/18 = 5/9\n  A did rest = 1-5/9 = 4/9\nStep 2: A worked = (4/9)÷(1/12) = 48/9 = 16/3 days\n  A left = 10 - 16/3 = 14/3 days early\n\nTRICK (LCM method):\nLCM(12,18)=36 → A=3/day, B=2/day\n\n|←── A worked ──→|← A left →|\n|  A+B together   | B alone   |\n|←──── 10 days total ────────→|\n\nB did 10×2=20, A did 36-20=16\nA worked 16/3d, left 10-16/3 = 14/3d early\n\nAnswer: A left 4⅔ days before completion ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 4100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 41,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_4"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=1/12, B=1/18 per day\n  B worked all 10 days = 10/18 = 5/9\n  A did rest = 1-5/9 = 4/9\nStep 2: A worked = (4/9)÷(1/12) = 48/9 = 16/3 days\n  A left = 10 - 16/3 = 14/3 days early\n\nTRICK (LCM method):\nLCM(12,18)=36 → A=3/day, B=2/day\n\n|←── A worked ──→|← A left →|\n|  A+B together   | B alone   |\n|←──── 10 days total ────────→|\n\nB did 10×2=20, A did 36-20=16\nA worked 16/3d, left 10-16/3 = 14/3d early\n\nAnswer: A left 4⅔ days before completion ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
