    {
      "id": "el_51",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 1362,
      "width": 375,
      "height": 288,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=2x of B → B=18d, so A=9d\n  A=1/9, B=1/18 per day\nStep 2: Together = 1/9+1/18 = 2/18+1/18 = 3/18 = 1/6\n  Time = 1÷(1/6) = 6 days\n\nTRICK (LCM method):\nLCM(9,18)=18 → A=2/day, B=1/day\n\n       (18) Total Work\n         |\n    -----+-----\n    |          |\n   (2)        (1)  ← 2+1 = 3/day\n   (9)       (18)\n    A          B\n\nTogether = 3/day → 18/3 = 6 days\n\nAnswer: 6 days ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 5100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 51,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_6"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=2x of B → B=18d, so A=9d\n  A=1/9, B=1/18 per day\nStep 2: Together = 1/9+1/18 = 2/18+1/18 = 3/18 = 1/6\n  Time = 1÷(1/6) = 6 days\n\nTRICK (LCM method):\nLCM(9,18)=18 → A=2/day, B=1/day\n\n       (18) Total Work\n         |\n    -----+-----\n    |          |\n   (2)        (1)  ← 2+1 = 3/day\n   (9)       (18)\n    A          B\n\nTogether = 3/day → 18/3 = 6 days\n\nAnswer: 6 days ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
