      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_56",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 1832,
      "width": 296,
      "height": 260,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Total work = 10×8×6 = 480 man-hrs\nStep 2: New setup: 15 men × 8 hrs/day\n  Per day = 15×8 = 120 man-hrs\n  Days = 480/120 = 4 days\n\nTRICK (MDH formula):\nM1×D1×H1 = M2×D2×H2\n10×8×6 = 15×D2×8\n480 = 120×D2 → D2 = 4\n\n  M1=10  D1=8  H1=6  →  480 man-hrs\n    ×      ×     ×\n  M2=15  D2=?  H2=8  →  480 man-hrs\n\nMore men + more hrs → fewer days\n\nAnswer: 4 days ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 5600,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 56,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_7"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Total work = 10×8×6 = 480 man-hrs\nStep 2: New setup: 15 men × 8 hrs/day\n  Per day = 15×8 = 120 man-hrs\n  Days = 480/120 = 4 days\n\nTRICK (MDH formula):\nM1×D1×H1 = M2×D2×H2\n10×8×6 = 15×D2×8\n480 = 120×D2 → D2 = 4\n\n  M1=10  D1=8  H1=6  →  480 man-hrs\n    ×      ×     ×\n  M2=15  D2=?  H2=8  →  480 man-hrs\n\nMore men + more hrs → fewer days\n\nAnswer: 4 days ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
