      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A can do a work in 20 days. He starts alone. After 5 days\nB joins him and they finish the remaining work in 6 days.\nIn how many days can B alone do the work?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_60",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1810,
      "width": 129,
      "height": 17,
      "text": "Solution:",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#2f9e44",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 6000,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 60,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_8"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Solution:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_61",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 1832,
      "width": 296,
      "height": 260,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=1/20. In 5d, A does 5/20=1/4\n  Remaining = 3/4 done by A+B in 6 days\nStep 2: (A+B) rate = (3/4)/6 = 3/24 = 1/8\n  B = 1/8 - 1/20 = 5/40-2/40 = 3/40\n  B alone = 40/3 = 13⅓ days\n\nTRICK (LCM units):\nWork=20, A=1/day. A does 5 in 5d\n\n|←── 5 days ──→|←── 6 days ──→|\n|  A alone      |  A + B       |\n|  5 units      |  15 units    |\n\nA+B = 15/6 = 2.5/day, B = 1.5/day\nB alone = 20/1.5 = 13⅓ days\n\nAnswer: B alone takes 13⅓ days ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 6100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 61,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_8"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=1/20. In 5d, A does 5/20=1/4\n  Remaining = 3/4 done by A+B in 6 days\nStep 2: (A+B) rate = (3/4)/6 = 3/24 = 1/8\n  B = 1/8 - 1/20 = 5/40-2/40 = 3/40\n  B alone = 40/3 = 13⅓ days\n\nTRICK (LCM units):\nWork=20, A=1/day. A does 5 in 5d\n\n|←── 5 days ──→|←── 6 days ──→|\n|  A alone      |  A + B       |\n|  5 units      |  15 units    |\n\nA+B = 15/6 = 2.5/day, B = 1.5/day\nB alone = 20/1.5 = 13⅓ days\n\nAnswer: B alone takes 13⅓ days ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
