    {
      "id": "el_71",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 2302,
      "width": 296,
      "height": 231,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=1/18. Does 1/3 work → time=6d\n  Remaining = 2/3, B finishes in 10d\nStep 2: B's rate = (2/3)/10 = 2/30 = 1/15\n  B alone = 15 days\n\nTRICK (LCM units):\nWork=18, A=1/day, A does 1/3×18=6 units\n\n|←── 6 days ──→|←── 10 days ──→|\n|  A works 1/3  |  B finishes   |\n|  6 units      |  12 units     |\n\nB = 12/10 = 1.2/day → B alone = 18/1.2\n\nAnswer: B alone takes 15 days ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 7100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 71,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_10"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=1/18. Does 1/3 work → time=6d\n  Remaining = 2/3, B finishes in 10d\nStep 2: B's rate = (2/3)/10 = 2/30 = 1/15\n  B alone = 15 days\n\nTRICK (LCM units):\nWork=18, A=1/day, A does 1/3×18=6 units\n\n|←── 6 days ──→|←── 10 days ──→|\n|  A works 1/3  |  B finishes   |\n|  6 units      |  12 units     |\n\nB = 12/10 = 1.2/day → B alone = 18/1.2\n\nAnswer: B alone takes 15 days ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
