    {
      "id": "el_74",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 2221,
      "width": 787,
      "height": 49,
      "text": "If 2 men = 3 women = 4 children in terms of work, and 6\nmen and 4 women can do a work in 10 days, how many days\nwill 3 men, 4 women, and 8 children take?",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 7400,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 74,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_11"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "If 2 men = 3 women = 4 children in terms of work, and 6\nmen and 4 women can do a work in 10 days, how many days\nwill 3 men, 4 women, and 8 children take?",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_75",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 2280,
      "width": 129,
      "height": 17,
      "text": "Solution:",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 13,
      "strokeColor": "#7048e8",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 7500,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 75,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_11"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Solution:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
      "id": "el_76",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 2302,
      "width": 310,
      "height": 274,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 2M=3W=4C → 1M=2C, 1W=4/3C\n  Group1: 6M+4W = 12C+16/3C = 52/3 C\n  Group2: 3M+4W+8C = 6+16/3+8 = 58/3 C\nStep 2: Work = (52/3)×10 = 520/3 child-days\n  Days = (520/3)÷(58/3) = 520/58 ≈ 8.97\n\nTRICK (ratio shortcut):\nConvert to smallest unit (children)\n\n  2 Men = 3 Women = 4 Children\n  1M=2C      1W=4/3C\n\n  Group1: 6M+4W = 12C+16/3C = 52/3 C\n  Group2: 3M+4W+8C = 6+16/3+8 = 58/3 C\n\nDays = (52/3 × 10) / (58/3) = 520/58\n\nAnswer: ~9 days (8.97) ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 7600,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 76,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_11"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: 2M=3W=4C → 1M=2C, 1W=4/3C\n  Group1: 6M+4W = 12C+16/3C = 52/3 C\n  Group2: 3M+4W+8C = 6+16/3+8 = 58/3 C\nStep 2: Work = (52/3)×10 = 520/3 child-days\n  Days = (520/3)÷(58/3) = 520/58 ≈ 8.97\n\nTRICK (ratio shortcut):\nConvert to smallest unit (children)\n\n  2 Men = 3 Women = 4 Children\n  1M=2C      1W=4/3C\n\n  Group1: 6M+4W = 12C+16/3C = 52/3 C\n  Group2: 3M+4W+8C = 6+16/3+8 = 58/3 C\n\nDays = (52/3 × 10) / (58/3) = 520/58\n\nAnswer: ~9 days (8.97) ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
    {
