    {
      "id": "el_81",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 2302,
      "width": 303,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Total work = 20×30 = 600 man-days\n  In 10d: 20×10 = 200 man-days done\nStep 2: Remaining = 600-200 = 400 man-days\n  Now 30 men → 400/30 = 13⅓ days\n\nTRICK (fraction approach):\nIn 10d, 20 men do 10/30=1/3 of work\nLeft=2/3, men=30 → D=20×30×(2/3)/30\n\n|←── 10 days ──→|←── 13⅓d ──→|\n|  20 men        |  30 men     |\n|  200 man-days  |  400 m-days |\n\n= 400/30 = 13⅓ more days\n\nAnswer: 13⅓ more days ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "angle": 0,
      "seed": 8100,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 81,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "groupIds": [
        "type_12"
      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Total work = 20×30 = 600 man-days\n  In 10d: 20×10 = 200 man-days done\nStep 2: Remaining = 600-200 = 400 man-days\n  Now 30 men → 400/30 = 13⅓ days\n\nTRICK (fraction approach):\nIn 10d, 20 men do 10/30=1/3 of work\nLeft=2/3, men=30 → D=20×30×(2/3)/30\n\n|←── 10 days ──→|←── 13⅓d ──→|\n|  20 men        |  30 men     |\n|  200 man-days  |  400 m-days |\n\n= 400/30 = 13⅓ more days\n\nAnswer: 13⅓ more days ✓",
