    {
      "id": "el_96",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1005,
      "y": 2758,
      "width": 281,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=1/12. Full 4d → 4/12=1/3 done\n  Left=2/3. Half eff=1/24 per day\nStep 2: Time = (2/3)÷(1/24) = 16 days\n  Total = 4+16 = 20 days\n\nTRICK (units method):\nWork=12, Full=1/day, Half=0.5/day\n\n|←── 4 days ──→|←── 16 days ──→|\n|  Full eff     |  Half eff     |\n|  4 units      |  8 units      |\n\nPhase1=4, Left=8, Phase2=8/0.5=16d\nTotal = 4+16 = 20 days\n\nAnswer: 20 days ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
