      ],
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=1/12. Full 4d → 4/12=1/3 done\n  Left=2/3. Half eff=1/24 per day\nStep 2: Time = (2/3)÷(1/24) = 16 days\n  Total = 4+16 = 20 days\n\nTRICK (units method):\nWork=12, Full=1/day, Half=0.5/day\n\n|←── 4 days ──→|←── 16 days ──→|\n|  Full eff     |  Half eff     |\n|  4 units      |  8 units      |\n\nPhase1=4, Left=8, Phase2=8/0.5=16d\nTotal = 4+16 = 20 days\n\nAnswer: 20 days ✓",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null
    },
