    {
      "id": "el_101",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 65,
      "y": 3214,
      "width": 274,
      "height": 245,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: Rate=1/15. In 3-day cycle:\n  Works 2d, off 1d → 2/15 per cycle\nStep 2: 7 cycles (21d) = 14/15 done\n  Left=1/15 → 1 more work day (day 22)\n\nTRICK (units method):\nWork=15, Eff=1/day\n\n|W |W |off|W |W |off|...\n|1 |1 | 0 |1 |1 | 0 |...\n  3-day cycle → 2 units done\n\n7 cycles=21d→14 done. Left=1\nDay 22: works → finishes!\n\nAnswer: 22 actual days ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
