    {
      "id": "el_106",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 535,
      "y": 3214,
      "width": 260,
      "height": 260,
      "text": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=10%/day, B=15%/day\n  Together = 10%+15% = 25% per day\nStep 2: Time = 100%/25% = 4 days\n\nTRICK (% shortcut):\nn days → (100/n)% per day\nx%/day → (100/x) days\n\n      (100%) Total Work\n         |\n    -----+-----\n  (10%)      (15%)  ← 25%/day\n    A          B\n\nCombined = 25%/day → 100/25 = 4 days\n\nAnswer: 4 days ✓",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 12,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "roughness": 0,
