      "originalText": "LOGIC:\nStep 1: A=10%/day, B=15%/day\n  Together = 10%+15% = 25% per day\nStep 2: Time = 100%/25% = 4 days\n\nTRICK (% shortcut):\nn days → (100/n)% per day\nx%/day → (100/x) days\n\n      (100%) Total Work\n         |\n    -----+-----\n  (10%)      (15%)  ← 25%/day\n    A          B\n\nCombined = 25%/day → 100/25 = 4 days\n\nAnswer: 4 days ✓",
